{"id": "1292776673489453107", "channel_id": "1292776673489453107", "type": 0, "author_id": "1051752197244866681", "author_name": "iceyss_", "author_bot": false, "content": "不是哥们，你口口声声最近产能紧张在忙重要的事，能不能给哥们透露一下到底在忙什么啊，在忙怎么数值膨胀骗氪和做出粪怪恶心人吗，这怎么最基本的角色文案都跟不上了啊，我真是不想说这么难听的但是你们最近怎么越来越一脸死相了啊，你这个最好是bug而不是你借着本源的名义不打算写了，环娜那边可是有这个文案的", "timestamp": "2024-10-07T09:12:57.589000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1292776673770737695", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-07-17-08-23-060_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 214584, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1292776673489453107/1292776673770737695/Screenshot_2024-10-07-17-08-23-060_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a004c19&is=69fefa99&hm=b1e112400ab675f364557730af462e46432553daf409abbe812a46ca53782468&"}, {"id": "1292776674248884254", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-07-17-08-26-526_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 216133, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1292776673489453107/1292776674248884254/Screenshot_2024-10-07-17-08-26-526_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a004c19&is=69fefa99&hm=adac718f02417d85be02d8291423eefd1644595a091de90f326f21afa284f8ab&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1292776673489453107", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "希洛的技能小故事呢？？？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
